Name: Deadly Strike
Dis: Deals 50000 damage to the Siege Target. Damage doubled if the target has less than 25% HP.

Name: Serial Pursuit
Dis: Deals damage to the Siege Target equal to 1.2% of HP lost.

Name: Heavy Bombardment
Dis: Deals damage to the Siege Target equal to 0.8% of max HP.

Name: Agile Ambush
Dis: Deals damage to the Siege Target equal to 1.2% of current HP.

Name: Battle Cry
Dis: Deals 60000 damage to the Siege Target.

Name: Skill Charge
Dis: Increase the effect of the next Stronghold Skill by 2.5x

Name: Point Hypertune
Dis: Grants 10000 Command Bureau Points when this is triggered.
